          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待为娘对吾儿细说从头："
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "抛下了母子们苦度春秋；"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "皆因是儿年小、家业空、盼只盼、数年之后、教子成名、好对我那孟氏坟丘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的儿呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿的父遭不幸中年夭寿"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为娘我勤纺织把光阴来度"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲教训儿谨受，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走近膝前说从头："
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎学那市井之徒无赖之尤！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿虽然年幼小心思浅陋"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有一辈圣贤空前绝后，"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待为娘学说古圣根由："
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到后来率门徒宣道德列国周游；"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "讲易删诗述作春秋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "立志勤学定把名留。"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿虽然年幼小心思浅陋"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿啊，你看那亘古以来，哪一个圣贤不从那少年经过。但是父母的教训，只许"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你读书养气，岂容学那市井之徒！况为娘盼子成人，教儿的心切；惟恐儿任气"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "纵性，攻乎异端，不得正道，失没根基。为娘所教儿的言语，须要紧记心头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "仲尼少年陈俎豆"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "设教杏坛制礼定乐"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿若是效法那先师指授"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩儿谨记在心。以往过错，望母亲恕过！"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为娘倒有个主意，你我母子何不迁移在城外乡村，离开这市井的繁华，以便儿"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "明心养性，你看如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩儿遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好个孝顺的儿呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为孤儿移性情循循善诱，"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "远屠沽近庄农为善的关头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "教为娘宽怀抱散虑消愁。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（仉氏、孟轲同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "孟轲→仉氏",
          "turns": 7
        },
        {
