    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "孟轲",
        "常守文"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（常守文上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "常守文",
          "line_type": "数板",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命苦身贫，命苦身贫，世人拿我不当人。只因我，衣不遮体，常常赤半身。饭"
        },
        {
          "character": "常守文",
          "line_type": "数板",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不能饱，每日只能吃半顿。为度残生给人照应坟。可怜我，饥寒困苦常与鬼为"
        },
        {
          "character": "常守文",
          "line_type": "数板",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "邻，常与鬼为邻！"
        },
        {
          "character": "常守文",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我常守文。就是这邹国人氏。祖居在这个村儿，给公卿大人们照管坟墓。因此"
        },
        {
          "character": "常守文",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人都叫我常守坟。只因我国和鲁国搭界，可恨那鲁国倚强欺弱，时常侵犯我国，"
        },
        {
          "character": "常守文",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "因此我国不断的向百姓们征兵征赋，闹得全国“老者转于沟壑，壮者散而之"
        },
        {
          "character": "常守文",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四方”了。就拿我们村儿说吧，人口萧条，住户减少。我要不是给公卿大夫们"
        },
        {
          "character": "常守文",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "照管坟墓，早就被征去当兵啦。这且不言，我们村儿里，新由城里搬来个孟老"
        },
        {
          "character": "常守文",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太太，带着个十来岁的小孩子，孤儿寡母，很是清苦。最奇怪的是那个小孩子，"
        },
        {
          "character": "常守文",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "每天愁眉泪眼，咳声叹气，自言自语，疯疯癫癫。那么点儿的小孩子，真仿"
        },
        {
          "character": "常守文",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "佛个五十多岁的人那么多愁多虑的样子。还不如我这穷小子没心没肺，得过且"
        },
        {
          "character": "常守文",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "过，随遇而安哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "常守文",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "近日里村落中炊烟减少，"
        },
        {
          "character": "常守文",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人口稀住户少景况萧条。"
        },
        {
          "character": "常守文",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "觉天宽与地阔并不心焦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（常守文笑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "常守文",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "富与贵贫与贱一个土包。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": "常守文",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "远远望见那个小孩来啦，待我听他说些什么！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孟轲上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叹光阴如过客百年非久，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朝复夕夕还朝日月轮流。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一抔土也不知几历春秋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "野花闲花满月愁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "触目伤心不自由。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "悲从中来泪湿衣袖，泪湿衣袖、我那亡父啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "抛下了母子们寡侣失俦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "青山绿水还依旧"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "凄风苦雨残碑朽"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "问天不语空搔首"
        },
        {
          "character": "常守文",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说这小孩，你有什么症候吧？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是坟少爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": "常守文",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好说您哪。我问问你，你天天这么愁眉苦脸的，为了什么呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老丈，你看蓬蒿遍野，古墓成堆。想人生在世，不过百年，无非如此。岂不令"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人伤心惨目，教我岂得不愁？"
        },
        {
          "character": "常守文",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我问问你，您今年高寿啦？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "年方十岁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "常守文",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "您才十岁，就打这个算盘，多早晚您才愁的完哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休得取笑。看前面青山隐隐，绿水迢迢，何不同去一观？"
        },
        {
          "character": "常守文",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我还有事，不能奉陪。公子请便吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此说，少陪了。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤愚千载知谁是，早晚蓬蒿共一丘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孟轲下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "常守文",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，只顾跟他瞎聊，我的晚饭还没准备出来哪。我得准备晚饭去！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（常守文下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "常守文→孟轲",
          "turns": 7
        },
        {
          "edge": "孟轲→常守文",
