    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "仉氏",
        "孟轲"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（仉氏、孟轲同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "荒郊外渺茫茫山明水秀，"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "村落里人烟少风景清幽。"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎奈他双眉锁整日忧愁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿呀，你我母子迁移在这村庄以内，看那些风清月白，水秀山明，正好畅意开"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怀，涵养那中和之气。怎么你，不是学那些埋葬的仪节，就是学那吊祭的悲哀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我看你小小的年纪，是这样抑郁不舒，岂不堕落了英雄志气！难道说，这村"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "庄居住，就不能悦性怡情了么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为孤儿避繁华迁移未久"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲所说言语，孩儿领会。岂不知这村居野处，悦性怡情；怎奈一见荒丘垒垒，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "古墓成堆，不由得痛彻心肺，想起去世的爹爹来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿待怎讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想起去世的爹爹来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（仉氏、孟轲同哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听我儿言悲惨壮心灰透，"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "三叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "亡父，孟轲，儿呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不由我肝肠断痛泪交流。"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又谁知反惹起儿思父的念头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "教为娘怎对那孟氏坟丘！"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿呀，如此说来，在这村中居住，倒是为娘的不是了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "娘本意避繁华为儿迁就"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倘若是儿有个天长地久"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩儿怎敢说母亲的不是！"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也罢！你我母子仍旧迁回城内，寻一清幽所在，儿好上进读书，栽培志气，你"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "道如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩儿遵命！"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此甚好。来，来，来，随为娘把行囊家具收拾起来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母子们因择地东奔西走，"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "避村居返城邑往复周流。"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "择一处好邻居教子回头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "仉氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿啊，随为娘来呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（仉氏、孟轲同下。）"
        }
      ],
